OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and outbreaks of rain in
OL,6,Fthe west at first. This spreading east
OL,7,Fand becoming heavy for a time. Then
OL,8,Fclearing to bright spells and showers
OL,9,Flater in the afternoon. Occasionally
OL,10,Fwindy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudier in the east with
OL,13,Fsome outbreaks of rain and drier
OL,14,Finterludes. Otherwise bright then
OL,15,Fclear spells and a few showers coming
OL,16,Fin from the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
