OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAny cloud and rain in the east
OL,6,Fsoon clearing. Otherwise bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells and scattered showers,
OL,8,Fmore frequent in the west and heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,13,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday, these heavy
OL,14,Fand thundery at times. Widespread
OL,15,Fcloud and rain arriving from the west
OL,16,Fon Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
